  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/805270/extras/da45a2caccea1bacdbef8f12c8e2bbc3.avif?t=1729299776\" width=616 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Experiment game creation in an easy, fast and fun way!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have fun Creating games without coding or Play tones of solo and multiplayer games shared by the community.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play&Create first-person, third-person, top-down, solo or multiplayer games</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create fast with a simple interface, without any code</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build dynamic, destructible online worlds with friends</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize visuals, rules, characters, powers, vehicles, cinematics, dialogues and more</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No limitations, zero farming required to unlock all tools & content</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Offline & Online multiplayer co-creation and play</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Share your games and prefabs on the Steam Workshop</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If your game stand out, have the possibility to publish on Steam directly</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playcraft is a great way to develop your creativity while having fun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Let's craft and play new games!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/805270/extras/da45a2caccea1bacdbef8f12c8e2bbc3.avif?t=1729299776\" width=616 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Experiment game creation in an easy, fast and fun way!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have fun Creating games without coding or Play tones of solo and multiplayer games shared by the community.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play&Create first-person, third-person, top-down, solo or multiplayer games</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create fast with a simple interface, without any code</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build dynamic, destructible online worlds with friends</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize visuals, rules, characters, powers, vehicles, cinematics, dialogues and more</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No limitations, zero farming required to unlock all tools & content</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Offline & Online multiplayer co-creation and play</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Share your games and prefabs on the Steam Workshop</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If your game stand out, have the possibility to publish on Steam directly</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playcraft is a great way to develop your creativity while having fun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Let's craft and play new games!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
